background-color: #ccc;"> there are stories</a> about hedge funds selling G=
ameStop=C2=A0calls at the peak and making a ton of money.) Meanwhile though=
 retail was mostly buying <em>puts=C2=A0</em>during GameStop=E2=80=99s big =
week, also betting that the stock would go down (or hedging the gains they =
