 talked</a> about <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/=
25393723.275721/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9uZXdzL25ld3NsZXR0ZXJzLzI=
