idth: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; backgr=
ound-color: #ccc;"> wants to do anyway</a>: reducing=C2=A0settlement times =
to reduce clearinghouse risk, improved reporting of short sales, more trans=
parency for off-exchange trading. None of these things have much to do with=
 what happened to GameStop that last week in January. Or here=E2=80=99s thi=
s:</p><blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Consideration should be give=
n to whether game-like features and celebratory animations that are likely =
intended to create positive feedback from trading lead investors to trade m=
ore than they would otherwise. In addition, payment for order flow and the =
incentives it creates may cause broker-dealers to find novel ways to increa=
se customer trading, including through the use of digital engagement practi=
ces.</p></blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Yeah, look.=C2=A0<em>In g=
eneral</em>, do retail brokerages have economic incentives to push more tra=
ding? Yes, definitely. Do little animations of confetti to celebrate a trad=
e make people more likely to trade? Sure, maybe, why not.=C2=A0<em>Did peop=
le buy tons and tons of GameStop in the last week of January because of the=
 game-like user experience of their brokerage apps?=C2=A0</em>No, of course=
 not, come on. The game of GameStop, in January 2021, was not about getting=
 to the top of Robinhood=E2=80=99s leader board or whatever. (Robinhood was=
 trying to=C2=A0<em>stop=C2=A0</em>people from trading GameStop that week! =
It actually=C2=A0<em>prevented=C2=A0</em>them from buying GameStop for a wh=
ile!) The game of GameStop was pervasive in society; if you were buying Gam=
eStop stock it was because you read about it on Reddit or on the front page=
 of every newspaper, or because you heard about it on every television news=
 show. There were at least <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.c=
om/click/25393723.275721/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cudGhld3JhcC5jb20vbWFrZS1pdC1nYW1lc3=
RvcC1hbGwtdGhlLWNvbXBldGluZy1maWxtLWFuZC10di1wcm9qZWN0cy1pbi10aGUtd29ya3MtY=
